Class AccountNumber

java.lang.Object
project1.AccountNumber
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<AccountNumber>
public class AccountNumber extends Object implements Comparable<AccountNumber>
A Account Number class for RU banking project that defines a unique 9-digit account number. 9-digit code = 3-digit area code + 2-digit account type + 4-digit random number
